title: Fellowes Spectra 95 and 125 Laminator
description:
User-friendly laminator for the home or home office
Hot lamination for 3-mil or 5-mil, as well as cold pouches
Release lever disengages pouch for re-centering or removal
Warms up in 4 minutes
Accommodates multiple document sizes
Auto shut-off prevents overheating when not in use
Includes laminating starter kit
1-year warranty

For More Info: http://www.fellowes.com/us/en/Products/Pages/product-listing.aspx?cat=BUSINESS-MACHINES&subcat=LAMINATING_MACHINES&tercat=PERSONAL_LAMINATING_MACHINES
